column4: CA 95823\rPhone Number916-689-2120\rPrincipalAbelardo Cordova\rE-mail AddressACordova@egusd.net\rWeb Sitehttp://blogs.egusd.net/leimbach/\rCounty-District-School(CDS) Code34673146077291\rSchool Description and Mission Statement (School Year 2019 - 2020)\rHerman Leimbach Elementary\r"Leimbach Lions R.O.A.R. with Pride"\rThe mission of Herman Leimbach Elementary is to provide an inclusive learning community that challenges all students to\rrealize their greatest learning potential and prepare them for college and career readiness.\rLeimbach staff are committed to building a culture that focuses on academic excellence and personal growth. Our goal is to\rprovide students with an exciting learning experience that encompasses the rigor of instruction within a safe and supportive\rclimate. Students receive a standards-based curriculum with extra support for those with special needs. We have an\racademic intervention team that works with designated students who show promise of rapid improvement or need intensive\rsupport. Learning Center staff assists those who need to make gains in reaching grade level standards. We also offer an\rafter school "ROAR Academy" where over 200 students receive assistance with homework and enrichment opportunities in\rtechnology
